headline: Why The Narrative Around DoorDash NasdaqGS DASH Is Shifting After Recent Analyst And Market Updates
summary: What Changed in the DoorDash Narrative DoorDash’s fair value estimate has been kept effectively steady, with only a fractional move from US$276.41 to US$276.39 per share, while the discount rate has inched up from 8.37% to about 8.40% and revenue growth expectations have been nudged from roughly 23.9% to 24.0%. These small adjustments reflect a tug of war between bullish views that point to solid order trends and new growth channels, and more cautious views that factor in heavier investment...
